http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/karnataka/Nairmalya-Ratha-flagged-off-in-Hassan/article14006084.ece

The awareness campaign on Nirmal Bharat Abhiyan was launched by the zilla panchayat here on Monday. The campaign consists of a procession by the Nairmalya Ratha for spreading public awareness about cleanliness and importance of Nirmal Bharat Abhiyan. Hemavati Manujath, president of the zilla panchayat, flagged off the drive.Chief Executive Officer of the zilla panchayat R. Venkatesh Kumar said that it had been decided to ensure that the district soon emerged as open-defecation free. “We are conducting awareness programmes to achieve the objective. We are looking forward to the involvement of public, non-governmental organisations, students and panchayat bodies for making the programme a success,” he said.The Nairmalya Ratha travels across the district with an audio system to spread the awareness on cleanliness.